<p><strong>2.</strong> In this example, we will use annotations so we have two ways to enable them.</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>UserServiceImplTest.java</span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
